name: Android Gallery Thumbnail Index
summary: A THUMBDATA4-1763508120 file is a data file created by the Gallery app included with select Android phones, such as the Samsung J7 and HTC Desire SV. It contains information about every thumbnail image Gallery has indexed, to help the app load the images more quickly. THUMBDATA4-1763508120 is stored in a device's hidden .THUMBNAILS folder, which is visible only when you've chosen to show hidden files and folders on your device.
